SUMMARY:Baby Got Back (Problems)
LOCATION:London
DESCRIPTION:In 2023\, Joe Leather was chasing his dreams of an Edinburgh Fr
 inge debut\, when...ping! A herniated disc! Some people survive shark attac
 ks\; Joe stretched too enthusiastically. Refusing to accept such a humble b
 eginning\, Joe rewrites history live onstage to find a 'back' story worthy 
 of the painful consequences. Baby Got Back (Problems) is a musical comedy a
 bout ambition\, bad timing and the absolute audacity of the human spine. It
 's a show for anyone who’s ever thought "this is going to be my year..." 
 then had to lie down for a while. Offie-winner Joe Leather blends musical c
 omedy\, puppetry and genre-bending storytelling in a show about pain\, perf
 ormance and the desperate human need to turn random suffering into a good t
 ale(bone).\nMore info: https://comedyatlas.app/comedy-atlas/event/baby-got-
 back-problems/
